</bibRefCitation>
, this study)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BC23699330EFFCCFF36F8D12057F854" blockId="9.[136,1452,1418,2056]" pageId="9" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis id="B909EA8B330EFFCCFF36F8D1200BF89D" box="[189,345,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="46">Known hosts:</emphasis>
On symptomatic twigs of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7D4D1A330EFFCCFD07F8D1221CF89D" authorityName="K.Koch" authorityYear="1869" baseAuthorityName="Wangenh." box="[652,846,1850,1877]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Juglandaceae" genus="Carya" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="9" pageNumber="46" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="illinoensis">
