<bibRefCitation id="EFEC4B68330EFFCCFCD1F8B4254BF8B1" author="Yang, Q. &amp; Fan, X. L. &amp; Guarnaccia, V. &amp; Tian, C. M." box="[858,1049,1886,1913]" pageId="9" pageNumber="46" pagination="97 - 149" refId="ref10010" refString="Yang, Q., Fan, X. L., Guarnaccia, V. &amp; Tian, C. M. (2018) High diversity of Diaporthe species associated with dieback diseases in China, with twelve new species described. MycoKeys 39: 97 - 149. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / mycokeys. 39.26914" type="journal article" year="2018">
