<bibRefCitation id="EFEC4B68330EFFCCFBAEF8B4258AF8B1" author="Guo, Y. S. &amp; Crous, P. W. &amp; Bai, Q. &amp; Fu, M. &amp; Yang, M. M. &amp; Wang, X. H. &amp; Du, Y. M. &amp; Hong, N. &amp; Xu, W. X. &amp; Wang, G. P." box="[1061,1240,1886,1913]" pageId="9" pageNumber="46" pagination="132 - 162" refId="ref7890" refString="Guo, Y. S., Crous, P. W., Bai, Q., Fu, M., Yang, M. M., Wang, X. H., Du, Y. M., Hong, N., Xu, W. X. &amp; Wang, G. P. (2020) High diversity of Diaporthe species associated with pear shoot canker in China. Persoonia-Molecular Phylogeny and Evolution of Fungi 45: 132 - 162. https: // doi. org / 10.3767 / persoonia. 2020.45.05" type="journal article" year="2020">
